en_US.project_summary: SNZ is a crypto-native and community-oriented incubator and venture capital firm. Active since 2014, the SNZ team has been dedicated to community building, incubation, and investment.

zh_CN.project_summary: SNZ 是一家以加密货币为基础、以社区为导向的孵化器和风险投资公司。自2014年开始活跃以来，SNZ团队一直致力于社区建设、孵化和投资。
